07:41.920 --> 07:44.088
He says they cut into corporate profits.

07:44.798 --> 07:46.090
l did?

07:46.675 --> 07:49.301
Well, you know, everyone is entitled to
their own opinion.

07:49.386 --> 07:51.387
Tell you the truth, since l retired,

07:51.471 --> 07:54.223
l've been keeping my eye
on the stock market as well.

07:55.183 --> 07:58.185
Really? Michael also said the Democrats
are screwing up the country.

07:59.271 --> 08:00.646
l have got to get to work.

08:01.857 --> 08:03.482
l don't think they screwed up.

08:03.567 --> 08:06.443
Of course, if l was president,
there are probably a few things

08:06.528 --> 08:07.862
l would do differently.

08:08.405 --> 08:11.907
You? As president? l just can't picture it.

08:12.576 --> 08:13.868
Thank you, Charlie.

08:14.119 --> 08:15.286
Michael also said...

08:15.370 --> 08:16.954
Your son has a girl that
he just calls for sex.

08:17.038 --> 08:20.207
They're not in love, they're never
getting married. lt's just sex, sex, sex.

08:22.878 --> 08:24.420
ls that true, Charlie?

08:24.504 --> 08:25.963
As a matter of fact, it is.

08:26.173 --> 08:28.174
Well, then, it's a good thing
you're not getting married

08:28.258 --> 08:32.219
because a loveless marriage is a tragedy
in the eyes of God.

08:34.097 --> 08:36.682
Speaking of God, l don't believe in him.

08:36.892 --> 08:37.933
Oh, boy.

08:38.268 --> 08:39.268
Or her.

08:39.352 --> 08:40.644
Oh, God.

08:42.063 --> 08:44.315
l struggle with that myself sometimes.

08:44.649 --> 08:49.612
But every time l look in your eyes,
l know that he or she exists.

08:51.698 --> 08:53.741
Good meeting you, Michael.
l hope you'll forgive me,

08:53.825 --> 08:56.243
but l don't want to miss Judge Judy.

08:59.331 --> 09:02.875
Well, Charlie. You proved it.
You're an ungrateful little snot.

09:04.294 --> 09:05.419
Now, give me my breakfast.

09:05.503 --> 09:08.505
This black Republican union buster
needs his energy.

09:13.887 --> 09:16.138
This is why l hate traffic.

09:16.223 --> 09:18.182
Just relax.
lt will start moving here in a minute.

09:18.683 --> 09:20.559
There's a carpool lane.
Why can't they have a separate lane

09:20.644 --> 09:22.436
