09:37.577 --> 09:40.412
l'm sorry, l'm sorry. Why don't we just talk?

09:41.456 --> 09:45.084
So, l didn't know l was going to
meet your dad this morning.

09:45.168 --> 09:46.835
He seems like such a nice guy.

09:47.254 --> 09:48.545
Yeah, thanks.

09:49.714 --> 09:52.466
He's like the nicest old man l've ever met.

09:53.093 --> 09:55.177
He's like Santa without a beard.

09:55.262 --> 09:56.470
All right.

10:00.976 --> 10:03.018
