10:10.151 --> 10:11.819
l mean, come on.
Look at his bumper stickers.

10:11.903 --> 10:14.446
"Coexist." "Visualize world peace."

10:14.531 --> 10:18.367
You want everyone to think you're nice,
but l know the truth, jerk face!

10:19.828 --> 10:22.329
Dude, what are you doing?

10:22.831 --> 10:24.248
l'm sorry.

10:26.501 --> 10:28.168
l let my dad get the best of me.

10:30.213 --> 10:32.006
Yeah. Perfect.

10:32.674 --> 10:35.092
lt's okay. Let me handle this. Girls,

10:36.594 --> 10:37.845
you're on.

10:39.764 --> 10:41.515
lt's a chick.

10:42.017 --> 10:44.643
Please be a lesbian.
Please be a lesbian. Please be a lesbian.

10:49.232 --> 10:51.859
That's a heck of an idea, Martin.

10:53.069 --> 10:54.611
