10:54.696 --> 10:56.947
Oh, your daddy and l were
just chewing the fat,

10:57.032 --> 10:59.908
talking about how hard
it is to get a job at our age.

11:00.201 --> 11:02.286
And l was talking about my road rage issues

11:02.370 --> 11:06.498
and how l should probably hire
a driver before l accidentally kill somebody.

11:06.583 --> 11:08.876
Because l really want to kill somebody.

11:09.627 --> 11:11.795
Well, l just thought maybe she
could toss Ed a few bucks

11:11.880 --> 11:13.130
and he could drive her around.

11:13.214 --> 11:16.925
Yeah, Dad, it's a nice idea, but
Lacey and Ed have a very complex dynamic.

11:17.010 --> 11:19.636
And there's a lot of emotional ramifications
to an arrangement like that.

11:19.721 --> 11:21.138
How's 20 bucks an hour?

11:21.222 --> 11:22.639
l'll do it for 30.

11:22.724 --> 11:26.560
Fifty if you want to listen to
that Arab music while l'm driving.

11:27.771 --> 11:31.148
