and l'm lndian.

11:31.232 --> 11:32.733
White people work for us now.

11:34.569 --> 11:37.321
Well, l got to go. Really nice meeting you.

11:37.405 --> 11:39.114
l hope you all get well soon.

11:39.240 --> 11:42.701
Hey, Dad. Before you go,
l have a big favor to ask.

11:42.786 --> 11:44.411
Sure.

11:45.163 --> 11:46.538
You want me happy, right?

11:46.623 --> 11:48.874
That's all l've ever wanted for you, Charlie.

11:48.958 --> 11:50.417
Of course.

11:51.461 --> 11:53.253
Would you be willing to
see my therapist with me

11:53.338 --> 11:55.214
