a look of disgust, turned your back and left.

12:33.795 --> 12:37.047
l would never do that to you.
Don't you remember what happened?

12:37.507 --> 12:39.550
Your cousin came to the ballpark to tell me

12:39.634 --> 12:43.720
Aunt Cecile got killed by a bus.
l had to leave. lt was an emergency.

12:44.472 --> 12:47.266
-Aunt Cecile got hit by a bus?
-Yes.

12:47.392 --> 12:48.976
Wasn't she the one who
was drunk all the time?

12:49.060 --> 12:50.060
Yes.

12:50.145 --> 12:53.105
At work, at home, and sadly, at the bus stop.

12:55.150 --> 12:56.483
You never told me that.

12:56.568 --> 13:00.529
This is very common. Two people often
remember the same incident differently.

13:00.613 --> 13:03.782
And Charlie, sometimes we
selectively remember.

13:03.867 --> 13:06.034
l suppose that's possible.

13:06.494 --> 13:09.746
