13:13.960 --> 13:15.544
l did smash the guitar.

13:15.628 --> 13:17.754
Thank you. Thank you.
l thought l was going crazy.

13:17.839 --> 13:20.716
But not because you were playing too loud.

13:20.800 --> 13:23.844
l smashed it because l'd warned you,
"lf you don't get your grades up,

13:23.928 --> 13:25.762
