13:25.847 --> 13:28.056
Okay. Okay. All right.
You know what? There's more.

13:28.600 --> 13:30.058
How about the time you took
the puppy away?

13:30.143 --> 13:31.894
l had to. lt died.

13:32.854 --> 13:34.229
You missed my graduation.

13:34.314 --> 13:35.314
l had to work.

13:35.440 --> 13:36.773
You made me shave my long hair.

13:36.858 --> 13:38.817
Because you had lice,
which you got from the puppy.

13:39.861 --> 13:41.612
