bad combination.

13:53.541 --> 13:55.042
Thank you.

13:55.126 --> 13:58.629
Son, it really hurts me to hear you say

13:58.713 --> 14:02.216
that you've been carrying around
all this pain for so long.

14:02.717 --> 14:04.968
l know l wasn't the perfect father,

14:05.053 --> 14:07.471
but l am not that guy you think l was.

14:08.223 --> 14:10.641
Maybe Kate's right.

14:10.725 --> 14:14.311
