14:19.984 --> 14:21.944
l tried your therapy.

14:22.028 --> 14:23.779
How about you trying mine?

14:28.076 --> 14:29.993
-Do it for Brett.
-Come on.

14:30.078 --> 14:31.286
-Do it.
-All right.

14:32.497 --> 14:35.999
