14:37.418 --> 14:39.169
Jimmy Cagney.

14:39.254 --> 14:41.964
-More.
-Do some Brando.

14:44.092 --> 14:45.759
"Are you an assassin?"

14:45.843 --> 14:47.636
"l'm a soldier."

14:47.720 --> 14:49.680
"You're neither.

14:49.764 --> 14:54.226
"You're an errand boy sent by
grocery clerks to collect a bill."

15:00.233 --> 15:01.733
l love that movie.

15:03.278 --> 15:06.780
You know, Charlie, if your father's
marital status ever changes,

15:06.864 --> 15:08.365
